lation":"And, indeed, [even] before thy time have [God's] apostles been derided, and for a while I gave rein to those who were [thus] bent on denying the truth: but then I took them to task - and how awesome was My retribution!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1739.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":34981,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدِ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/013_032_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34982,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱسْتُهْزِئَ","translation":"বিদ্রুপ করা হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_032_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34983,"position":3,"arabic":"بِرُسُلٍۢ","translation":"সাথে রাসূলদের","audioUrl":"wbw/013_032_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34984,"position":4,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"থেকেই","audioUrl":"wbw/013_032_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34985,"position":5,"arabic":"قَبْلِكَ","translation":"তোমার পূর্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/013_032_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34986,"position":6,"arabic":"فَأَمْلَيْتُ","translation":"অতঃপর আমি অবকাশ দিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_032_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34987,"position":7,"arabic":"لِلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদেরকে) জন্যে যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_032_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34988,"position":8,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","translation":"অস্বীকার করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_032_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34989,"position":9,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/013_032_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34990,"position":10,"arabic":"أَخَذْتُهُمْ ۖ","translation":"তাদের আমি পাকড়াও করেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_032_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34992,"position":11,"arabic":"فَكَيْفَ","translation":"অতঃপর (দেখো) কেমন","audioUrl":"wbw/013_032_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34993,"position":12,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/013_032_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34994,"position":13,"arabic":"عِقَابِ","translation":"আমার শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_032_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":34995,"position":14,"arabic":"٣٢","translation":"(৩২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":33,"arabic":"أَفَمَنْ هُوَ قَآئِمٌ عَلَىٰ كُلِّ نَفْسٍۭ بِمَا كَسَبَتْ ۗ وَجَعَلُوا۟ لِلَّهِ شُرَكَآءَ قُلْ سَمُّوهُمْ ۚ أَمْ تُنَبِّـُٔونَهُۥ بِمَا لَا يَعْلَمُ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ أَم بِظَٰهِرٍۢ مِّنَ ٱلْقَوْلِ ۗ بَلْ زُيِّنَ لِلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ مَكْرُهُمْ وَصُدُّوا۟ عَنِ ٱلسَّبِيلِ ۗ وَمَن يُضْلِلِ ٱللَّهُ فَمَا لَهُۥ مِنْ هَادٍۢ","translation":"IS, THEN, HE who has every living being in His almighty care, [dealing with each] according to what it deserves -[is, then, He like anything else that exists]? And yet, they ascribe to other beings a share in God's divinity! Say: \"Give them any name [you please]: but do you [really think that you could] inform Him of anything on earth that He does not know-or [do you] but play with words?, Nay, goodly seems their false imagery to those who are bent on denying the truth, and so they are turned away from the [right] path: and he whom God lets go astray can never find any guide.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1740.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":35825,"position":1,"arabic":"أَفَمَنْ","translation":"তবে কি সেই (সত্ত্বা)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_033_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35826,"position":2,"arabic":"هُوَ","translation":"যিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_033_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35827,"position":3,"arabic":"قَآئِمٌ","translation":"দন্ডায়মান (পর্যবেক্ষক)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_033_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35828,"position":4,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/013_033_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35829,"position":5,"arabic":"كُلِّ","translation":"প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/013_033_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35830,"position":6,"arabic":"نَفْسٍۭ","translation":"মানুষ","audioUrl":"wbw/013_033_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":35831,"position":7,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"ঐ স